<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Oct1931"><font color="red">8 October 1931</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver):  My wife feels homesick for her Kensington flat (Grrr! Chickens from Backer&apos;s) &hellip; There was a long article in <i>Harper&apos;s</i>; in Huddleston&apos;s book, in Axel&apos;s Castle etc &hellip; Natheless I work all day, smiling unto mineself </div>
